Package org.ibm.sterling.mule.oms.config

Class BasicConfiguration

java.lang.Object
org.ibm.sterling.mule.oms.config.BasicConfiguration
@Operations(BasicOperations.class)
@ConnectionProviders(OMSConnectionProvider.class)
@RequiresEntitlement(name="IBM Corp")
public class BasicConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents an extension configuration, values set in this class are commonly used across multiple operations since they represent something core from the extension.
